title: Turkey's President Erdogan seals election victory to enter third decade in power
description: Analysts saw the 69-year-old Erdogan's victory as all but in the bag after the first vote on May 14.

title: Global audience demand for streaming Asian movies, series grows with hits like 'Squid Game'
description: Viewership for Asian TV content is growing on streaming services in the U.S., following popular hits like "Squid Game" and "Everything Everywhere All At Once."

title: Now Boarding: Why airlines are turning to bigger planes to beat airport congestion
description: On this episode of "Now Boarding," CNBC discusses how airlines are turning to bigger planes as airport congestion and a pilot shortage limit new flights.

title: Turkey votes in runoff election after candidates double down on nationalism and fear
description: Country analysts are all but certain of an Erdogan victory.

title: White House and Republicans reach a tentative deal to avoid U.S. default
description: House Republicans have reached a tentative deal with the White House to address the nation's debt ceiling and avoid a default.
